data.description:
*** BACK ON MARKET - Buyers Contingent home failed to sell ********   Charming spacious ranch style home in treasured Golden Acres. Large fenced yard with mature trees, creating a lovely home. Complete with year round sun-room and adjacent wood deck.

Three bedrooms on the first floor with  one and a half baths, large living room with attached dining, huge oak unit kitchen with further dining space, access to garage.

Almost finished lower level with separate entrance, large bedroom/work space, with full bathroom ( shower). Additional area plumbed for a kitchenette, Fireplace behind wall.

Additional room with laundry area complete with laundry Shute from upper level, furnace and wash basin and fitted vacuum system.

New a/c in 2021
Three ceiling fans on ground floor
Security system
Thermal windows
Central Vacuum
Wide driveway
